flowchart LR
  EV[Veiculo eletrico] --> HCA[GoodWe HCA G2]
  RFID[RFID / App] --> HCA
  HCA --> NET[LAN / Wi-Fi / RS-485]
  NET --> SEMS[SEMS+ / Modbus TCP]
  SEMS --> ING[Adapter GoodWe]
  SIM[Simulador de sessoes] --> ING
  ING --> LOG[Event log auditavel]
  LOG --> API[API EV ChargeOps]
  API --> DB[(PostgreSQL)]
  API --> RATEIO[Motor de rateio]
  DB --> RATEIO
  RATEIO --> FAT[Faturas individuais]
  DB --> IA[Servicos de IA]
  IA --> ALERTAS[Previsao e anomalias]
  FAT --> GESTOR[Dashboard gestor]
  FAT --> USUARIO[Portal do usuario]
  ALERTAS --> GESTOR
  OCM[Open Charge Map] -.-> API
  PLACES[Google Places evChargeOptions] -.-> API
  ANEEL[ANEEL Open Data] -.-> API
  IBGE[IBGE Localidades] -.-> API

